Cheng5 1-cham7-a2 cheng5-su5 bo5 joa7 un2-teng7, ma7 eng2-hiong2 tioh8 ka-ti7 e5 seng-oah8. cheng3-keng kong2--khi2-lai5, ui3 8--goeh8 khai-si2 chiah8 thau5-lou7, ka-ti7 pun2-te2 e5 hak8-seng sim-thai3 to7 it-tit8 bo5 thiau5-cheng2--koe3-lai5, tak8-kang thau3-cha2 long2 chiok oan3-chheh--e5.
