Kui goeh8-jit8 loh8--lai5, long2 kiu ti7 ka-ti7 ou-am3 e5 siu7 lai7-te2, it-tit8 kau3 ke teh thi5 chiau2 teh kio3, te7 1 loh8 kng-soann3 chhio7--loh8-lai5 e5 si5, chiah chai-iann2, m7-tann7 ai3 thau2-pang3 ka-ti7 e5 koe3-khi3, koh ai3 thau2-pang3 ka-ti7 e5 sim.
Chit-cham7-a2 sim cheng7--loh8-lai5, tauh8-tauh8-a2 kiann5 jip8-khi3 ka-ti7 e5 sim, ka7 ka-ti7 e5 choan5-pou7 long2 ou2--chhut-lai5, phou ti7 jit8-thau5 e7-kha phak8. Ti7 chia, u7 1-koa2 si7 ka-ti7 m7-goan7 khi3 bin7-tui3--e5, in-ui7 e7 kiann-hiann5 e7 kian3-siau3. M7-koh chim-chiok hoan2-seng2 kiam2-tho2 liau2-au7 e7 hoat-hian7, kiann-lang5--e5 ka7 seh8--koe3 liau2-au7, to7-si7 1-e5 sin e5 khai-si2.
Chin-chiann3 bin7-tui3 ka-ti7 e5 ou-am3, chiah u7 chai5-tiau7 kiann5 ng3 kong-beng5.
Chit kui2 kang, thau3-cha2 khi2--lai5 e5 si5, sim-cheng5 hoat-seng hoa3-hak8 pian3-hoa3, pian3 gah kap eng2-koe3 bo5 kang7-khoan2. Chit-chun7 goa2 chiah hoat-hian7, cho3-lang5 siong7 oh ma7 siong7 kan2-tan--e5, to7-si7 thiau7-chian3 ka-ti7, hou7 leng5-hun5 chhin-chhiunn7 hai2-eng2, hou7 bah-the2 chhin-chhiunn7 koan5-soann, hou7 sin5-keng chhin-chhiunn7 kui3-hong, hiah-ni7 bin2-kam2 iong2-chai7 ng3 cheng5 chhiong--khi3.
Goa2 chiok ai3 chit-ma2 e5 ka-ti7, sui-bong2 koh u7 koa2 khih-kak, tan2 goa2 ka7 pou2 hou7 oan5-boan2.
